quran[11{c,v,t}:
17,105,aur hum ne is quran ko sachaai ke sath nazilkiya hai aur woh sachaai ke sath nazil howa aur ( ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam ) hum ne tum ko sirf khushkhabri dainay wala aur dar sunanay wala bana kar bheja hai
17,106,aur hum ne quran ko juzo juazo karkay nazilkiya hai taakay tum logon ko tehr tehr kar parh kar sunaaoo aur hum ne is ko aahista aahista utaara hai
17,107,keh do ke tum is par imaan lao ya nah lao ( yeh fi nafsa haq hai ) jin logon ko is se pehlay ilm ( kitaab ) diya hai. jab woh un ko parh kar sunaya jata hai to woh thoriyon ke bil sjday mein gir parte hain
17,108,aur kehte hain ke hamara perwar-digaar pak hai be shak hamaray perwar-digaar ka wada poora ho kar raha
17,109,aur woh thoriyon ke bil gir parte hain ( aur ) rotay jatay hain aur is se un ko aur ziyada aajzi peda hoti hai
17,110,keh do ke tum ( khuda ko ) allah ( ke naam se ) poukaro ya rehman ( ke naam se ) jis naam se poukaro is ke sab achay naam hain. aur namaz nah buland aawaz se parho aur nah aahista balkay is ke beech ka tareeqa ikhtiyar karo
17,111,aur kaho ke sab tareef khuda hi ko hai jis ne nah to kisi ko beta banaya hai aur nah is ki badshahi mein koi shareek hai aur nah is wajah se ke woh aajiz o natawan hai koi is ka madadgaar hai aur is ko bara jaan kar is ki barayi karte raho
18,1,sab tareef khuda hi ko hai jis ne apne bande ( Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam ) par ( yeh ) kitaab nazil ki aur is mein kisi terhan ki kajji ( aur paicheedgi ) nah rakhi
18,2,seedhi ( aur salees utari ) taakay logon ko azaab sakht se jo is ki taraf se ( anay wala ) hai dry aur mominoun ko jo naik amal karte hain khushkhabri sunaye ke unn ke liye ( un ke kamon ka ) naik badla ( yani ) bahisht hai
18,3,jis mein woh aubdul -aabaad rahen ge
18,4,aur un logon ko bhi dry jo kehte hain ke khuda ne ( kisi ko ) beta bana liya hai
